{
  "stem": "27285.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then you were thrown out in '44-- in October '44 to this horrible, horrible place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So in Auschwitz, we went through all these things that you had to go through to be counted again and again and again, and you stand out in the open.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And one of these days they took 200 of us to throw us into another cattle train or something and back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Before that, had you done any work there?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "What was the routine, like you say--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Auschwitz?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We did not work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We just were-- no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Deprived of anything and thrown into some barracks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't-- I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think the first day, you don't get food at all.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But this really didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It really didn't-- the whole-- the other things are so much stronger, the impressions.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I cannot tell you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because it was not the problem of hunger any-- with me, personally, so I cannot relate to this if we got food or didn't get food.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A few days, a week maybe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember, because we were chosen to go on to work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was already '44 October, so-- so we were thrown again into a cattle-- in a cattle train or whatever.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Do you call it a cattle train?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Cattle car, something.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and-- and to Germany, which was close to Dresden-- something between Dresden and Kremnitz, which was not such a good [INAUDIBLE] on, but it was-- there, there was a-- a-- a munition factory where we were supposed to work.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But again, when we arrived, there were already 300, 400 women there mostly from Poland and Hungary.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
